Description: multi_language_digits_converter
        ===================
        
        
        **Multi Language Digits Converter** The Multi Language Digits Converter allows you to convert digits between different languages including Bangla, Hindi, Urdu, Malayalam, Thai, Arabic & etc. 
        
        ----------
        
        Features
        ===================
        
        > - Conver English int to other languages and return a string
        
        Install
        ===================
        We recommend install pyconvertdigits through pip install using Python 3.
        
        > $ pip install multi_language_digits_converter
        
        Example
        ===================
        
        To see available languages:
        
			import multi_language_digits_converter
			convertDigits = multi_language_digits_converter.conDigits()
			languages = convertDigits.available()
			print(languages)
			

            #output: ['Bangla', 'Hindi', 'Urdu', 'Malayalam', 'Thai', 'Arabic', 'Farsi', 'Japanese', 'Korean', 'Telugu', 'Tamil', 'Russian', 'Greek', 'Hebrew']
        To convert English to other languages:
        
            import pyconvertdigits
            convertDigits = pyconvertdigits.conDigits()
        
			converted_japanese = convertDigits.to_japanese(1234567890)
			print(converted_japanese)

			 = convertDigits.to_urdu(1234567890)
			print(converted_urdu)

			converted_hindi = convertDigits.to_hindi(1234567890)
			print(converted_hindi)
		
